- Hi, Bugsy.

04:17.860 --> 04:20.168
<i>We interrupt this program
to bring you a news flash.</i>

04:20.579 --> 04:23.617
<i>We have reports of an incident
on the Lower East side...</i>

04:23.780 --> 04:27.853
<i>involving the man known
as Roxy the Weasel.</i>

04:28.100 --> 04:31.137
<i>Believed to be a member
of the gang of mobster king...</i>

04:31.300 --> 04:33.768
<i>Fat Sam Stacette.
Robinson was the victim of a...</i>

04:33.940 --> 04:35.658
